Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/middleware.html

Demonstrates the usage of postSave hooks in RxDB for series, parallel, and asynchronous operations after a document has been saved.

```javascript
// series
myCollection.postSave(function(plainData, rxDocument){}, false);

// parallel
myCollection.postSave(function(plainData, rxDocument){}, true);

// async
